Sodiq Oyeleke The Nigeria Police Force has announced N10 million cash rewards for information on two suspects. The Police Force Public Relations Officer, Frank Mba, announced this on Thursday. [READ ALSO] Ooni to Igboho: You are forgiven, I am behind you Mba, who attached the pictures of the suspects in a post on the police social media handles, said, “N0,000,000 awaits anyone with useful information on the whereabouts of the persons in the photo captured on the CCTV at a crime scene.” 